 <a href="#other">other details</a> about my office/working setup.<h1 id="software--services">Software &amp; Services</h1><ul><li>The list of <a href="/mac-tools#title">software applications</a> I use on my Mac.<li>A <a href="/infosec-tools#title">huge list of infosec-related tools</a>, many of which I use.<li>For social media and news, I use…<ul><li><a href="/an-ode-to-rss#title">RSS</a><li><a href="/notes/2025/01/10/gotosocial-on-knt-host">GoToSocial</a><li><a href="/mastodon#title">Mastodon</a><li><a href="/threadiversal-travel#title">Threadiverse</a> apps (e.g. Lemmy, Kbin)<li><a href="https://www.apple.com/apple-news/">Apple News</a><li>Other <em>thread-ey</em> platforms (e.g. <a href="https://lobste.rs/">Lobste.rs</a>, <a href="https://tildes.net/">Tildes</a>, <a href="https://squabblr.co">Squabblr</a>, <a href="https://news.ycombinator.com/news">Hacker News</a>)</ul><li>Here are the <a href="#whats-on-my-iphone">apps I keep on my iPhone</a> home screen<li>For mail, I have moved to <a href="https://proton.me">Proton</a> Mail<li>For music, I use <a href="https://music.apple.com">Apple Music</a><li>I have a few other things I can <a href="#referrals">refer you to here</a><li>My Mastodon instance <a href="https://shellsharks.social/">shellsharks.social</a> is hosted by <a href="https://masto.host">Masto.host</a><li>My <a href="https://gotosocial.org">GoToSocial</a> instance <a href="https://malici.ous.computer">malici.ous.computer</a> is hosted by <a href="https://www.knthost.com">K&amp;T Host</a></ul><h1 id="shellsharks-tech-stack">Shellsharks Tech Stack</h1><p>I’ve summarized my tech stack, discussed my motivation for the site and professed my love for the <a href="https://indieweb.org">IndieWeb</a> at the resources listed below (respectively).<ul><li><strong>Tech Stack</strong>: <a href="https://shellsharks.com/humans.txt">humans.txt</a>, <a href="/blogging-from-ipad#hosting">hosting</a>, <a href="/dynamize-jekyll#title">Jekyll</a><li><strong>Motivation</strong>: <a href="/blogging-from-ipad#title">Shellsharks summary</a>, <a href="/you-should-blog#title">Why I Blog</a>, <a href="/get-to-know-my-blog#title">Get To Know My Blog</a><li><strong>IndieWeb</strong>: <a href="/indieweb.txt">IndieWeb.txt</a>, <a href="/indieweb">Intro to IndieWeb</a></ul><p>A more full-featured <a href="/architecture">ARCHITECTURE.md</a> readout is available.<h1 id="desk-setup-hardware">Desk Setup (Hardware)</h1><p>Before establishing my <strong>/uses</strong> page, I had tracked my <a href="/desk-setup-2021#title">hardware/desk setup here</a>. <em>Now</em>, I’ll maintain an updated list below.<p><strong>*</strong> First, check out my library of <a href="/cybersecurity-library#title">infosec books</a> (<em>that I have totally read</em>).<p><img src="https://shellsharks-images.s3.amazonaws.com/desksetup.jpeg" alt="Desk Setup" /><ul><li><i class="ph ph-desk"></i> <strong>Desk</strong> : IKEA <a href="https://www.ikea.com/us/en/p/skogsta-dining-table-acacia-70419264/">SKOGSTA 92” Dining Table</a><li><i class="ph ph-chair"></i> <strong>Chair</strong> : Secretlab <a href="https://secretlab.co/collections/titan-series#titan_2020_softweave-charcoal_blue">TITAN</a> (SoftWeave Charcoal Blue)<li><i class="ph ph-computer-tower"></i> <strong>Desktop Computer</strong> (<em>Primary</em>) : Apple <a href="https://support.apple.com/kb/SP797?locale=en_US">Mac Pro 7,1 (2019)</a> [3.2 GHz 16-Core Intel Xeon W CPU, 96 GB 2933 MHz DDR4 Memory, AMD Radeon Pro Vega II 32 GB GPU, 2 TB SSD + 2 TB Cache SSD, Ventura 13.5.1]<li><i class="ph ph-keyboard"></i> <strong>Keyboard</strong> : Apple <a href="https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MLA22LL/A/magic-keyboard-us-english">Magic Keyboard</a><li><strong>Trackpad</strong> : Apple <a href="https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MJ2R2LL/A/magic-trackpad-2-silver">Magic Trackpad 2</a> [ <em>Silver</em> ]<li><i class="ph ph-mouse"></i> <strong>Mouse</strong> : Apple <a href="https://www.apple.com/shop/product/MLA02LL/A/magic-mouse-2-